{"tid":1074673,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]幼園校長失蹤逾兩日 !","createTime":"2019-03-23T14:27:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-24T14:21:13.000Z","uid":116709,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"db8a23ebf60c6fb6a85eabfd697e0eed15807f11","tid":1074673,"uid":116709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T14:27:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190323/s00001/1553346613038/幼園校長失蹤逾兩日\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190323%2Fs00001%2F1553346613038%2F%E5%B9%BC%E5%9C%92%E6%A0%A1%E9%95%B7%E5%A4%B1%E8%B9%A4%E9%80%BE%E5%85%A9%E6%97%A5&d=INFrb%2BpCZNVkt1J9J2ljECPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=b78789d3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190323%2Fs00001%2F1553346613038%2F%E5%B9%BC%E5%9C%92%E6%A0%A1%E9%95%B7%E5%A4%B1%E8%B9%A4%E9%80%BE%E5%85%A9%E6%97%A5&h=456ef0c0\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190323/s00001/1553346613038/幼園校長失蹤逾兩日</a><br />\n<br />\n任職葵涌一間幼稚園校長、現年45歲的女子余倩瑛失蹤，警方今日呼籲市民提供消息，表示余倩瑛周四（21日）上午離開她位於藍田連德道的住所後失蹤，其家人同日報警。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，余倩瑛身高約1.63米，體重約50公斤，瘦身材，尖面形，黃皮膚及蓄長直黑髮。她最後露面時身穿淺藍色外套、黑色長褲、黑色鞋、戴眼鏡及攜有紫色手袋。任何人如有余倩瑛消息或曾見過她，請致電3661 0321或9886 0060或電郵至rmpu-ke-2@police.gov.hk與東九龍總區失蹤人口調查組，或與任何一間警署聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n咁猛料, 又係學校出事<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8439cea059f9bbc0fa53945b17e08f59eafce4d0","tid":1074673,"uid":213607,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T14:41:18.000Z","msg":"校長判官"},{"pid":"64b51d4d15034803f1bfa032176a01faacc7881d","tid":1074673,"uid":116709,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T14:56:09.000Z","msg":"之前老師跳, 今次校長失蹤<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一件傳一件<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hk